<br />
Here is what I would like to see most, and yes, most of it has already been mentioned, so I'm just adding agreement.<br />
<br />
1) Improve our harvest spell and AA to be a percentage of total mana pool. Perhaps 20% for the spell and 40% for the AA.<br />
<br />
2) Mass Teleport. I see no reason why this shouldn't be implemented.<br />
<br />
3) Adjustments to our resist factors on all spells. Since we rely 100% on our spells and are supposedly the Masters of Direct Damage, you would think that we would be better at getting our spells to land. Nothing is worse than spending 5 seconds and 1k'ish mana on a big spell that gets resisted while the melee classes poke, hack and slash away. Standard resist adjustment is -10 when it should really be more like -45.  Even with -50 from pyro and -12 from clicky staff thats -107...not at all unreasonable. Even an AA line that would improve our resist adjustments significantly would be awesome.</div>
